{"tid":2448880,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇返工兄弟試過收工前拎哂啲嘢入廁所屙屎，夠鐘出返嚟就撞到上司仲跟埋佢返office ?","createTime":"2021-03-16T08:37:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-16T08:58:08.000Z","uid":40930,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f4f86ece8cce8f16e7bbdbe55fc50e615974b61e","tid":2448880,"uid":40930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T08:37:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />臨收工走去屙屎都係為咗可以準時走<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />行出門口見到上司，佢又搵啲工事同你講<br />\n<br />\n講下講下就帶埋你返office<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/linguistic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後又坐返埋位做嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以每次夠鐘都會留意下廁所有冇動靜先走出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n究竟有咩方法阻到上司去屙屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8032e8731efa0a043ff3cd0055e0c41547cbc27e","tid":2448880,"uid":70465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T08:58:08.000Z","msg":"仲唔係比我捉到你<br />\n知你籠野啦, 次次扮屙屎想閃人<br />\n我係專登係門口捕你既"}]}